      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BEAR THE BRUNT (1) has placed at the last four runs, the latest finishing second (22.50) at Geelong. Form here sound including two wins. Rates strongly and will go close from the inside draw. PLAY LAB (2) started big odds last time where he hit the ground running and was never headed, leading throughout to win by 4 lengths over 400, at this track (22.46). Solid record here at the distance winning five races. Must be included in calculations. WHY NOT IRIS (6) hit the ground running from the squeeze draw with a sensational early split last time, but run over late and missed the frame when a 3 length fifth (26.32) over 460m at this track. The form from her last run is stacking up nicely. Can measure up this time. GALLOPING JESSIE (4) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
